{"tid":944362,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"團隊成功破解人面解鎖：Samsung 、One Plus 、LG 都輸了給 iPhone","createTime":"2018-12-17T05:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T05:59:02.000Z","uid":40119,"like":40,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"a064c4680ef4a1c0557736fee8e36a47fdfc79a3","tid":944362,"uid":40119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"應該一堆AnFan入嚟話唔係for你日常用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.techapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/960x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techapple.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F960x0.jpg&h=2b2d79dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在 Apple  FaceID 推出的時侯，已經有不少人嘗試把它破解。但因為利用各種感應器去進行偵測，這不是簡單印一張相片就可以把它搞定的。雖然 BKAV 號稱可以利用一個面具把 FaceID 完全破解，但年內都沒有人再次利用「科技」挑戰成功（長得像不算啦），令不少團隊都希望驗證一下容貌解鎖的安全性。<br />\n<br />\n在媒體界也有一些人希望進行深入報導，早前 Forbes 的記者 Thomas Brewster 就把自己的外表利用 3D 打印出來，測試不同的 Android 手機和 iPhone 的安全性，結果是 Android 陣營慘敗。這次 Thomas 測試的手機包括 Samsung Galaxy Note 8 、Samsung Galaxy S9 、LG G7 ThinQ、OnePlus6 以及 iPhone X ，嘗試破解的方式就是利用 3D 打印打印頭像，希望能騙過系統的驗證，事結果是除了 iPhone X 之外，高精度的「人頭」還是能能騙過 Android 手機。團隊估計原因是 Android 手機仍然採用面部象徵辨識，而 iPhone 是結合了紅外線高精度的掃瞄，令結果更為準確。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n這對於黑客、警方甚至政府來說可能是一件「喜事」，畢竟他們要取得你的個人資料，只要帶你進行一次 3D 掃瞄就好，在美國的第五修正案的保護當中，亦沒有提到對於指紋及 FaceID 類加密的保護，可見現在對於生物特徵加密仍然有可改進的空間。<br />\n<br />\n對於一些敏感的資料，我們還是多加幾重安全認證，或是乾脆用只有自己知道的密碼才更安全，對吧。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n引用來源：TechCrunch<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.techapple.com/archives/27824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techapple.com%2Farchives%2F27824&d=k2qrr0G%2Ba244%2By6O%2BacQjDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=a6efd686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.techapple.com/archives/27824</a>"},{"pid":"772cad3137bae2470e0dfe5cc899b947e8fd3d48","tid":944362,"uid":37399,"like":115,"dislike":11,"score":104,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T05:56:05.000Z","msg":"an機如果要做到iPhone咁精密嘅面部解鎖就會好慢<br />\n<br />\n咁樣an狗就冇得打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f73941d014948f704d766855da26bc8f3fd825","tid":944362,"uid":109383,"like":49,"dislike":12,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T05:58:31.000Z","msg":"Apple世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論安全性 可解鎖角度 解鎖速度都完美屌打其他廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6daf35afca1fe8ece63653238e3e6620a1ec1f","tid":944362,"uid":40119,"like":39,"dislike":8,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"772cad3137bae2470e0dfe5cc899b947e8fd3d48","tid":944362,"uid":37399,"like":115,"dislike":11,"score":104,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T05:56:05.000Z","msg":"an機如果要做到iPhone咁精密嘅面部解鎖就會好慢<br />\n<br />\n咁樣an狗就冇得打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T06:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAndroid好自由好開放，好多rom刷有得root裝咩都得咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3524d0f2a4f8ed0e0b56894aed61186748f1917b","tid":944362,"uid":7854,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T06:06:41.000Z","msg":"faceid.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfingerprint.jpg"},{"pid":"4c4525e72867a32c579ec29334fb65d1d301373b","tid":944362,"uid":5787,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ae6daf35afca1fe8ece63653238e3e6620a1ec1f","tid":944362,"uid":40119,"like":39,"dislike":8,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"772cad3137bae